# Client-side
<client>
<server>
http
</server>
 <name>
HTTP, proxy, site+proxy auth and Location: to new host using location-trusted
 </name>
 <command>
http://first.host.it.is/we/want/that/page/234 -x %HOSTIP:%HTTPPORT --user iam:myself --proxy-user testing:this --location-trusted
</command>
</client>

